    {"order": 29, "block_type": "text", "content": "POINT ワキガは〇〇症と判明。汗を止めるだけは無意味な理由。", "heading_level": "h2", "tag_hint": "h2", "is_cta_block": false},
    {"order": 30, "block_type": "text", "content": "汗を止めるだけでは無意味である理由。なぜだかわかりますか？", "heading_level": "h3", "tag_hint": "h3", "is_cta_block": false},
    {"order": 31, "block_type": "image", "media_url": "https://file.mysquadbeyond.com/lazy.png", "alt_text": "lazy placeholder", "is_cta_block": false},
    {"order": 32, "block_type": "text", "content": "実は、ワキガは\"腋臭症\"という病気だったんです。", "heading_level": "h3", "tag_hint": "h3", "is_cta_block": false},
    {"order": 33, "block_type": "image", "media_url": "https://file.mysquadbeyond.com/lazy.png", "alt_text": "lazy placeholder", "is_cta_block": false},
    {"order": 34, "block_type": "text", "content": "そして、本当の原因は皮膚に潜む2種類の菌", "heading_level": "h3", "tag_hint": "h3", "is_cta_block": false},
    {"order": 35, "block_type": "image", "media_url": "https://file.mysquadbeyond.com/lazy.png", "alt_text": "lazy placeholder", "is_cta_block": false},
    {"order": 36, "block_type": "image", "media_url": "https://file.mysquadbeyond.com/lazy.png", "alt_text": "lazy placeholder", "is_cta_block": false},
    {"order": 37, "block_type": "text", "content": "これらの菌が汗に含まれるニオイ成分を分解", "heading_level": "h3", "tag_hint": "h3", "is_cta_block": false},
    {"order": 38, "block_type": "image", "media_url": "https://file.mysquadbeyond.com/lazy.png", "alt_text": "lazy placeholder", "is_cta_block": false},
    {"order": 39, "block_type": "text", "content": "その結果、ワキガのツーンとしたニオイが発生するんです。特に、厄介なのは", "heading_level": "h3", "tag_hint": "h3", "is_cta_block": false},
    {"order": 40, "block_type": "image", "media_url": "https://file.mysquadbeyond.com/lazy.png", "alt_text": "lazy placeholder", "is_cta_block": false},
    {"order": 41, "block_type": "text", "content": "毛穴の奥に潜むため肌の表面をケアするだけでは成分が届きにくい...", "heading_level": "h3", "tag_hint": "h3", "is_cta_block": false},
    {"order": 42, "block_type": "text", "content": "だから、市販品では対策が難しいんです。", "heading_level": "h3", "tag_hint": "h3", "is_cta_block": false},
    {"order": 43, "block_type": "image", "media_url": "https://file.mysquadbeyond.com/lazy.png", "alt_text": "lazy placeholder", "is_cta_block": false},
    {"order": 44, "block_type": "text", "content": "つまり、菌がいる限り、ワキガ臭が発生するということ。", "heading_level": "h3", "tag_hint": "h3", "is_cta_block": false},
    {"order": 45, "block_type": "image", "media_url": "https://file.mysquadbeyond.com/lazy.png", "alt_text": "lazy placeholder", "is_cta_block": false},
    {"order": 46, "block_type": "text", "content": "手術は菌に注目してないんだ....", "heading_level": "h3", "tag_hint": "h3", "is_cta_block": false},
